    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Saphonecrus jejuensis Kang & Lobato-Vila, sp. nov. female paratype: A) habitus in lateral view; B) head in anterior view; C) head in posterior view; D) antenna; E) head in dorsal view; F) mesosoma in dorsal view; G) head and mesosoma in lateral view; H) fore wing; I) propodeum; J) propleuron; K) tarsal claw; L) detail of the syntergite punctuation; M) gall. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7191031/files/figure.png" ;
